<--Task1-->
when for loop becomes infinite
      public class InfiniteForLoop {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        for (int i = 0; i >= 0; i++) {
            System.out.println("Loop Run Infinitely");
        }
    }
}
Output:-
         Loop Run Infinitely
         Loop Run Infinitely
         Loop Run Infinitely
         Loop Run Infinitely   Loop Run Infinitely        
         .......
         .......
         ..............
         ............
